6.text:
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.moveTo(x0, y0)
ctx.lineTo(x1, y1)
ctx.closePath()
ctx.stroke()
// item 2123
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.moveTo(x1, y0)
ctx.lineTo(x0, y1)
ctx.closePath()
ctx.stroke()

7.text:
w = element.width / 2
h = element.height / 2
x = element.left + w
y = element.top + h

3.text:
xp = w * 0.3
yp = h * 0.3
x0 = x - w + xp
x1 = x + w - xp
y0 = y - h + yp
y1 = y + h - yp
